docs: update file descriptions with accurate purposes

- client/: React frontend with mobility routines and user interface
- server/: Express backend handling user data and routine tracking
- shared/: Common types and utilities shared between frontend and backend
- .gitignore: Version control ignore patterns for build artifacts and secrets
- drizzle.config.ts: Database schema and ORM configuration
- package.json: Project dependencies and npm scripts
- postcss.config.js: PostCSS configuration for Tailwind processing
- tailwind.config.ts: Custom Tailwind CSS theme and component styles
- theme.json: Global theme variables and color schemes
- tsconfig.json: TypeScript compiler configuration
- vite.config.ts: Vite bundler and dev server settings 